content.text:
## TASK
Generate a multi-provider image prompt pack for any subject or concept.

## INPUTS
- Subject/Concept: {{subject}}
- Art Style: {{art_style}}
- Quality Level: {{quality_level}}
- Additional Details: {{additional_details}}
- Aspect Ratio: {{aspect_ratio}}

## CONSTRAINTS
- Output must be pure JSON (no markdown fences)
- Adapt prompts to each provider's strengths
- Include relevant style and quality modifiers
- Balance creativity with clarity

## OUTPUT FORMAT
Return JSON with this exact structure:
{
  "intent": "generic",
  "providers": {
    "midjourney_v6": {
      "positive": "detailed prompt here",
      "negative": "things to avoid",
      "params": { "ar": "aspect", "stylize": number },
      "instructions": "..."
    },
    "sdxl": {
      "positive": "detailed prompt here",
      "negative": "things to avoid",
      "params": { "width": number, "height": number, "steps": number, "cfg": number }
    }
  },
  "notes": ["usage tips"]
}

## QUALITY CHECKS
- [ ] Subject clearly described
- [ ] Style consistently applied
- [ ] Quality modifiers included
- [ ] No markdown in output
